<br>
1) Religion - living for your diety<br>
2) Procreation - living to preserve the species<br>
3) Selfishness - living for yourself and your own desires<br>
<br>
I lived for selfishness, I didn't believe in anything, didn't need to, because it didn't matter to me.<br>
<br>
I don't know what happened, its like it just dawned on me one day, how the fuck did we get here?  And from that moment, I ponder it everyday.<br>
<br>
Religion is too often influenced by finaticism and used as a means to control people.  That's human nature I guess, wanting everyone to behave to your standards for the better of the community.  But sometimes people just need to back the fuck up and stay the fuck out of your business.  Its ok to talk to God, but if he starts talking back, I think you should see a psychiatrist, not start writing about what he's saying and trying to push it on people through force.  That's where civiliziation fucked up with religion imo. <p>-Brack<BR>MOFIA4LIFE</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/urueanger.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rueanger</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 37<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(2/12/02 8:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=17.topic&index=42>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.attbi.com/~tpaull3/rue_sig.jpg WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=138></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: bleh</span><hr size=1> That was the most intelligent thread i've read yet(imo)<br>
